<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="apart-from">apart from</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>除…外 (别无)；若不：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Apart from them, I had no one to talk to.
除了他们，没有人和我说话。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>除…外 (尚有)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Apart from providing warmth, what was fire used for?
除了用来取暖，火还有什么用处？</p><footer>外 研⑦ – 6</footer></div></div>